{
  "stem": "27759.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if they lived through it, they'd go and establish these beach heads, and if they lived through it, they got their freedom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they would only allow them to establish beach heads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't allow them to go into the cities and towns, because they were bank robbers, safe crackers, and everything else in these Rangers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were supposed to be hardened like a Marine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Killers, stone killers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the prisoners here in the United States-- the Alcatraz's and all those prisons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so then after that, when they pulled up out, we were attached to the first division.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we went in the first French town [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Saint-Lo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Saint-Lo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-T-L-O.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Saint-Lo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the first French town to fall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went in, but the first invasion pushed us out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Germany pushed us back out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then while the 1st Division was regrouping, they sent us in with the 29th Infantry Division.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The 29th Infantry Division went in and re-took Saint-Lo and held it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after they had retook Saint-Lo, there was one side or one building standing right there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything else was rubble.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went up from Saint-Lo to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All those towns in southern France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Normandy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had read about Normandy in the geography books and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the opportunity to see it and see how those people lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they treated us all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was difficult.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you take a lot of people in Normandy, even to this day, dislike what the Americans did, because we had tear up towns.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, routing those Nazis out of there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't like us for tearing up their towns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because at least their towns were intact when the Germans occupied them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
